<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reset Your Password - Fifty Firsts Wellness</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .reset-title {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .reset-message {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .otp-box {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
        border: 2px solid #e74c3c;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 25px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .otp-title {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #e74c3c;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .otp-code {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #e74c3c;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        background: white;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 2px dashed #e74c3c;
      }

      .security-warning {
        background-color: #f8d7da;
        border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        color: #721c24;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .steps {
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .step-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
      }

      .step-number {
        background: #e74c3c;
        color: white;
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-right: 15px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .step-text {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #2c3e50;
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer-text {
        font-size: 12px;
        opacity: 0.8;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }

      .expiry-note {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        color: #856404;
        font-size: 14px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .manual-entry {
        background-color: #e8f4fd;
        border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        color: #0c5460;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 10px;
          border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header,
        .content,
        .footer {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .reset-title {
          font-size: 20px;
        }

        .otp-code {
          font-size: 24px;
          letter-spacing: 4px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">üîê Fifty Firsts Wellness</div>
        <div class="tagline">Secure Your Account</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="reset-title">Reset Your Password, <%= firstName %>! üîê</h1>

        <p class="reset-message">
          We received a request to reset your password for your Fifty Firsts
          Wellness account. Use the verification code below to complete the
          process.
        </p>

        <div class="otp-box">
          <div class="otp-title">üî¢ Your Verification Code</div>
          <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
          <p>Enter this 6-digit code in the password reset form to continue.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="expiry-note">
          <strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong> This verification code will expire in
          15 minutes for security reasons.
        </div>

        <div class="manual-entry">
          <strong>üìù Manual Entry:</strong> If the code above doesn't work,
          please copy and paste it manually: <strong><%= otp %></strong>
        </div>

        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Copy the verification code</strong> shown above
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Return to the password reset page</strong> and enter the
              code
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <strong>Create a new secure password</strong> and confirm the
              change
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="security-warning">
          <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Alert:</strong> If you didn't request this
          password reset, please ignore this email and contact our support team
          immediately. Your account security is our top priority.
        </div>

        <p
          style="
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
          "
        >
          Having trouble? Contact our support team and we'll help you regain
          access to your account.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p class="footer-text">
          ¬© 2024 Fifty Firsts Wellness. All rights reserved.<br />
          Protecting your wellness journey with secure accounts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
